Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:06.06,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在朝着宇宙尽头的进发之中　度过蜜月的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.69,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这段路途实在过于遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.86,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.37,sign_Serif,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\pos(544,970)}通过星门后\N\N{\fs100}第 70 日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.79,Default,16,0,0,0,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.21,Default,16,0,0,5,,都已经过去这么多天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.25,Default,16,0,0,5,,但我既没有感到饥饿也不会困乏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:31.59,Default,16,0,0,0,,我会就这样变成叫龙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:32.51,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:35.93,Default,16,0,0,0,,一点也不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:38.26,Default,16,0,0,0,,感觉就像变成了你的一部分一样{鮟鱇人}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.93,Default,16,0,1250,0,,在你的体内慢慢深入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.94,Default,16,0,1250,0,,就连你的感受我都能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:45.90,Default,Z2,0,1250,0,,我也是啊　Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.77,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.65,Default,16,0,0,0,,零贰　上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:57.28,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,来吧　Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.66,Default-Top,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要将两人的翅膀并成一对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.38,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们就可以飞到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.96,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们现在可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.13,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.97,sign_33134_360_Episode_1,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,210)}最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.97,sign_33134_361_Alone_and_Loneso,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(966.4,480)}别让我走
