Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.43,sign_Vertical - R,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有朝一日　一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.43,sign_Vertical - B,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(886.6,541.6)}有朝一日　一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.61,Default,G,0,0,0,,跑这么快　小心摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:44.77,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:48.11,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:49.28,Default,16,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.99,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:53.45,Default,16,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:55.95,Default,16,0,0,0,,我的名字是...
